ual/zh/language.types.mixed.php" class="type mixed" style="color:#EAB766">mixed</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Gets the value of a static class property, if <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">class</span>   is given, or the value of an instance property, if <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">instance</span>   is given.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.uopz-get-property-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <dl>       <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">class</span></dt>    <dd>     <p class="para">      The name of the class.     </p>    </dd>          <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">instance</span></dt>    <dd>     <p class="para">      The object instance.     </p>    </dd>          <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">property</span></dt>    <dd>     <p class="para">      The name of the property.     </p>    </dd>     </dl> </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.uopz-get-property-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns the value of the class or instance property, or <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.null">null</a></span></strong> if the property   is not defined.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.uopz-get-property-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <div class="example" id="uopz-get-property.example.basic">   <p><strong>示例 #1 Basic <span class="function"><strong>uopz_get_property()</strong></span> Usage</strong></p>   <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br></span><span style="color: #007700">class </span><span style="color: #9876AA">Foo </span><span style="color: #007700">{<br>    private static </span><span style="co